  <p>
    Now you can use the components from Palette and drag them to Mockup Screen to add then in your app and use Properties tab to change look/properties of the component. You can also add External Files like Images, Fonts, Pdf, Json, Etc. By Clicking on the Assets Button on the Top Right Corner.&nbsp;
